Question: Is the man in the bottom or in the top of the picture?

Reference Answer: top

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n250821.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=GET(image=IMAGE)
IMAGE0=CROP_BELOW(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='man')
ANSWER0=COUNT(box=BOX1)
ANSWER1=EVAL(expr="'bottom' if {ANSWER0} > 0 else 'top'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER1)
```
